reviewText: This concert album of MBLAQ is great.  I've watched it at least 6 times since I got it and will continue to watch it over and over.  I love it.  There are 3 DVDs and a photo book in the package.  Keep on keepin' on, MBLAQ, I love you.  All of you! I've been wanting this album for quite a while and now I HAVE IT - YEAH!!!!
